ntiated by neurons in the auditory cortex, providing a\nhypothesis for mid-level neuronal computation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2017 02:00:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Jan 2017 16:34:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 27 Jan 2017 19:21:10 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 15 May 2017 21:39:01 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sun, 15 Oct 2017 02:18:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-17"}
