 with poorer data in the\nmid-infrared. The basic results for these systems appear qualitatively similar,\nyet the constraints on the dust location and the grain sizes are weaker.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2017 11:35:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Jan 2017 11:47:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-01"}
