\nkeV$ (2\\%); CHDM for decay redshift $z_{\\rm decay} = 10^5$ (5\\%); ULA for mass\n$m_a = 10^{-24} \\, \\rm eV$ (3\\%). We also briefly discuss the detectability of\nthis deviation in light of the upcoming CMB experiment PIXIE, which might have\nthe sensitivity to detect this signal from the pre-recombination phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2017 11:45:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 30 Jan 2017 10:27:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 7 Jul 2017 06:48:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-10"}
